<h3 id="_7-偏好概率模型" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_7-偏好概率模型"><span>7. 偏好概率模型</span></a></h3>
<p>代入<strong>Bradley-Terry模型</strong>：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mi>p</mi><mi>β</mi><mo>∗</mo></msubsup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>≻</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>exp</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mi>β</mi><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>π</mi><mtext>ref</mtext></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><msup><mi>π</mi><mo>∗</mo></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi>β</mi><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>Z</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>exp</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo>⋅</mo><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>exp</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo>⋅</mo><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">p_\beta^*(y_1 \succ y_2 | x) = \frac{\exp\left( \beta \log \frac{\pi_{\text{ref}}(y_1|x)}{\pi^*(y_1|x)} + \beta \log Z(x) \right)}{\exp(\cdot) + \exp(\cdot)}
