<p><strong>简化后</strong>（利用<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>Z</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Z(x)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">Z</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>抵消）：</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mi>p</mi><mi>β</mi><mo>∗</mo></msubsup><mo>=</mo><mi>σ</mi><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mi>β</mi><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>π</mi><mtext>ref</mtext></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><msup><mi>π</mi><mo>∗</mo></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mi>β</mi><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>π</mi><mtext>ref</mtext></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><msup><mi>π</mi><mo>∗</mo></msup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">p_\beta^* = \sigma\left( \beta \log \frac{\pi_{\text{ref}}(y_1|x)}{\pi^*(y_1|x)} - \beta \log \frac{\pi_{\text{ref}}(y_2|x)}{\pi^*(y_2|x)} \right)
